cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with dense captioning in images. It also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it generates captions in natural language. The use of multi-scale message propagation and attribute grounding suggests that it may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the experiments are conducted on a visual dataset, indicating that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
